snippet.title: DARK DECEPTION: MONSTERS & MORTALS - HOUSE OF ASHES DLC OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
The House of Ashes DLC is now available on Steam (and coming soon to Epic Game Store)! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1825941/Monsters__Mortals__House_of_Ashes/
The base Monsters & Mortals game is required to play all DLCs:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266690/Dark_Deception_Monsters__Mortals/

Original House of Ashes tracks by:  Jason Graves
Monsters & Mortals cover music by: Daniel Dombrowsky
Video Editing by: Vincent Livings
